import React from 'react';
import { HStack, Button, Flex, Heading, Input, InputGroup, InputRightElement } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import { useNavigate, useParams } from 'react-router-dom';
import './App.css'


function ChatWindow() {

    let navigate = useNavigate();
    const redirectDataAnalytics = () => {
        return navigate("/data-analytics")
    }
    const redirectTextChat = () => {
        return navigate("/text-chat")
    }
    const { id } = useParams();

    return (
        <Flex flexDir="column" minH='100vh'>
            <header>
                <HStack justify="center">
                    <Button onClick={redirectDataAnalytics}>Data Analytics</Button>
                    <Button onClick={redirectTextChat}>Text Chat</Button>
                </HStack>
            </header>
            <Flex justify="center" flexDir='column'>
                <HStack>
                    <Heading>Group Chat {id}</Heading>
                    <Button>Back</Button>
                </HStack>
                <Flex flexDir='column'>
                    <Flex
                        flexDir='column'
                        position='absolute'
                        top='0'
                        left='0'
                        right='0'
                        bottom='2.5em'>

                    </Flex>
                    <InputGroup size='md'>
                        <Input
                            pr='4.5rem'
                            type='text'
                            placeholder='Type your message'
                            id='message'
                        />
                        <InputRightElement width='4.5rem'>
                            <Button h='1.75rem' size='sm'>
                                Send
                            </Button>
                        </InputRightElement>
                    </InputGroup>
                </Flex>

            </Flex>
        </Flex>
    );
}

export default ChatWindow;
